ere Norge rundt i en Hiace er noe som h\u00f8rer ungdommen til. Hvis ikke noen tilbyr oss masse penger. Da stiller vi opp.", "Byscenen l\u00f8rdag 26. november. Gjesteartister: Per Borten, Truls Lorentzen og Frank Reppen. Oppvarming: Grand Fuzz."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "51296f8f40c90b69b9b5e5c292db560cbc4ab3d7c9794fff0cc2c1fe20d3b6f7"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T21:48:24.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "\u00d8l, rock og krangling var hovedingrediensene i The School. L\u00f8rdag gjenforenes de for \u00e9n kveld."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article13843479.ece/tp80ta/ALTERNATES/w980-default/TheSchool15.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/2ba50717cde641e9756cebdac86fff9b8fa79944.jpg?59709c6f"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Det var en enorm romance og heftig krangling om hverandre -adressa.no", "Breaket p\u00e5 Bylarm", "Sekser p\u00e5 \u00d8ya", "- Trodde vi hadde tatt syre"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "2ba50717cde641e9756cebdac86fff9b8fa79944"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Luftforsvarets musikkorps", "Byscenen", "konsert", "Brukbar/Bl\u00e6st"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Luftforsvarets musikkorps,Byscenen,konsert,Brukbar/Bl\u00e6st"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["kranglet", "bandet", "enorm romance", "heftig krangling", "konsert", "hverandre"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["\u00f8ya", "nine inch nails", "hiace", "quartfestivalen", "spinal tap", "the school", "bylarm", "svartlamoen", "luftforsvarets", "byscenen", "nordfjoreid", "per borten", "brukbar", "espionage", "bl\u00e6st", "destructive sounds", "ramp", "\u00f8